            <p>
            <pb n="1v"/>
               <lb n="1"/><g ref="sym:spiral-left" type="symbol">*</g> svasti vijayaskandhāvārāt kamalanīyāgr<unclear>ā</unclear>hā<unclear>ra</unclear>vāsakāt prasabhapraṇatām<unclear>i</unclear>trāṇāṁ <gap reason="illegible" quantity="9" unit="character"/>
