               <lb n="3" break="no"/>rāgo nuraktam<orig>o</orig>labhṛtamitraśreṇībalāvāptarājyaśrīḥ paramamāheśvara<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śrīsenāpat<unclear>i</unclear><gap reason="illegible" quantity="3" unit="character"/>
               <lb n="4"/>tasya sutas taccaraṇarajoruṇāvanatapavitrīkṛtaśirāḥ śirovanataśatrucūḍāma<unclear>ṇiprabhā</unclear>
