               <lb n="16"/><unclear>Ekadhā</unclear>rikāp<choice><sic>ā</sic><corr>a</corr></choice>rottarataḥ uttarānakāparataḥ durbb<unclear>e</unclear>ṭakadakṣiṇataḥ rājya<unclear>mi</unclear>trānaka
               <lb n="17" break="no"/>padraṁ mātāpitroḫ puṇyāpyāyanārttham ātmanaś caihikā<unclear>m</unclear>uṣmikayathābhilaṣitaphalāvāpti
               <lb n="18" break="no"/>nimittam ācandrārk<choice><sic>t</sic><corr>k</corr></choice>ārṇṇavakṣitisthitisaritparvvatasamakālīnaṁ putrap<orig>o</orig><unclear>t</unclear>trānvayabhogyaṁ bali
