               <lb n="20" break="no"/>brāhmaṇakumārāya bhāgurisagotrāya maitrāyaṇikasabrahmacāriṇe Udakātisargge
               <lb n="21" break="no"/>ṇa brahmadāyam atisṛṣṭaṁ</p> <p>yato syocitayā brahmadeyasthityā bhuñjataḥ kṛṣatas samā
               <lb n="22" break="no"/>vāsayataḥ pradiśataś ca na kaiścit svalpāpy ābādhā vicāraṇā vā kāryyāsmadvaṅśajair āgā
               <lb n="23" break="no"/>minṛpatibhiś cāyam asmaddāyo numantavyaḥ paripālayitavyaś ca yaś cācchindyād ācchidyamā
               <lb n="24" break="no"/>naṁ vānumodeT sa paṁcabhir mmahāpātakais sopapātakais sa<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>yuktas syād</p> <p>api cātra vyāsagī<unclear>tāḥ</unclear>
               <lb n="25"/>ślokā bhavanti</p>
                     <lg n="1" met="anuṣṭubh">
                        <l n="ab">ṣaṣṭiṁ varṣasahasrāṇi svargge modati bhūmidaḥ</l>
                        <l n="cd">Ācchettā cānumantā <unclear>ca</unclear>
               <lb n="26"/>tāny eva narake vaseT</l></lg>
                     <lg n="2" met="anuṣṭubh">
                        <l n="ab">svadattāṁ paradattāṁ vā yo hareta vasundharāṁ</l>
                        <l n="cd">gavāṁ śatasahasras<unclear>y</unclear>a ha<unclear>ntuḥ</unclear>
               <lb n="27"/>prāpnoti kilbiṣaM</l></lg>
